        <h2>MathTool Demo (Velocity)</h2>

        This example demonstrates the loading of tools from within the template
        using a tool loader tool.<br>
        <br>
        Example: Load the MathTool into the context with key "math":<br>
        <code>&#35;set (&#36;math = &#36;toolLoader.load("org.apache.velocity.tools.generic.MathTool"))</code><br><br>

        #set ($math = $toolLoader.load("org.apache.velocity.tools.generic.MathTool"))
    
        Some of the functions provided by MathTool:<br>
    
        <table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4">
            <tr>
                <td>\$math.min(345, 765)</td><td>$math.min(345, 765)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>\$math.max(345, 765)</td><td>$math.max(345, 765)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>\$math.random(0, 999)</td><td>$math.random(0, 999)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>\$math.pow(2, 8)</td><td>$math.pow(2, 8)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>\$math.abs(-123)</td><td>$math.abs(-123)</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

